Create users with Postman

Create a user:

    Post to:
        localhost:3000/signup

    Body: (x-www-form-urlencoded)
        email: john@gmail.com
        password: john
        role: basic

Create an admin:

    Post to:
        localhost:3000/signup

    Body: (x-www-form-urlencoded)
        email: admin@example.com
        password: administrator
        role: admin